{"tid":1714790,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中聯辦真係好撚鬼鼠","createTime":"2019-11-13T02:51:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T04:03:12.000Z","uid":275230,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6930f4a3939bd02425a58ba687dd5c087b5ac7","tid":1714790,"uid":275230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:51:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n11月10號中聯辦出左個咁嘅通知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SnwMLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SnwMLb.png&h=d3ba9e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMsTZ5H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMsTZ5H.png&h=8ce5ebf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住第二日就開始搞中大<br />\n今日深圳共青團又話開放佢哋啲地方比NDS避難<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiBhHi7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiBhHi7.png&h=966c24f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\npopo都配合埋幫佢哋走佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSYDrL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSYDrL8.png&h=7e69bcb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實佢哋係咪一早夾好曬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等班天上人走左上去<br />\n大學就可以比佢哋任搞？</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"223de5cc558908cf91032b7ebf22abfee5df0dd0","tid":1714790,"uid":312125,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:54:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">［文宣入！］返工搭鐵受襲、催淚彈影響健康、女學生返學俾狗捉，<strong>請文宣製圖向怕死嘅打工仔、家長、學生宣傳三罷</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n林鄭連續兩日叫大家唔好罷工罷課，證明罷工罷課係佢春袋，然而差佬不斷製造罷工罷課條件，文宣請行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請文宣組以<span style=\"color: red;\">黑警返工時間突襲旺角站無差別襲擊勤力返工人士</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">中午中環射催淚彈</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">警察街上捉返學嘅女學生</span>、<span style=\"color: gold;\">以及警察話上堂等於非法集結</span>，做罷工罷課文宣圖<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">警告堅持要返工返學嘅人，即將面對惡犬強姦殺人滅口嘅危險，在網上廣傳！</span><br />\n<blockquote> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8oPyZO5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8oPyZO5.jpg&h=3f965005&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FJQN4pc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFJQN4pc.jpg&h=87289d57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1713400\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1713400</a>"},{"pid":"0e885753955e2ddd0ac2b291c3bfd9da2a24daf5","tid":1714790,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3d6930f4a3939bd02425a58ba687dd5c087b5ac7","tid":1714790,"uid":275230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:51:56.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n11月10號中聯辦出左個咁嘅通知<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8SnwMLb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8SnwMLb.png&h=d3ba9e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZMsTZ5H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZMsTZ5H.png&h=8ce5ebf3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n跟住第二日就開始搞中大<br />\n今日深圳共青團又話開放佢哋啲地方比NDS避難<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tiBhHi7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtiBhHi7.png&h=966c24f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\npopo都配合埋幫佢哋走佬<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FSYDrL8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFSYDrL8.png&h=7e69bcb0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其實佢哋係咪一早夾好曬<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">等班天上人走左上去<br />\n大學就可以比佢哋任搞？</span></span></strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:54:23.000Z","msg":"想殺人<br />\n靠哂記者"},{"pid":"2245fc650f48551502c9e6767dacfdcfbfd6b205","tid":1714790,"uid":104165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T02:58:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src